<div>
<p>At the ORC, we want to make sure that you can have fun, be safe, and have the best rental experience possible.&nbsp; Here are a few quick policies and guidelines that we use, as well as a copy of our rental agreement used whenever you rent equipment from us.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Reservations</strong></span></p>
<p>Reservations can be placed up to 30 days in advance.&nbsp; You can make a reservation by calling (208) 496-7337.&nbsp; You can also visit us in the store during regular hours.&nbsp; There are some exceptions for reserving equipment.&nbsp; Contact us with any specific questions.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Prices and Payment</strong></span></p>
<p>All rental prices are subject to change without notice.&nbsp; We offer multi-day rental discounts for specific equipment.&nbsp; You can view our pricing guides or contact us with specific questions.<br /><br />We&nbsp;accept cash, check, credit cards&nbsp;or campus account.&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Rental Agreement</strong></span></p>
<p><a href="Documents/outdoor-resource-center/Signature Pad Info.pdf" target="_blank">ORC Rental Agreement&nbsp;</a></p>
